OL,5, A security guard spying for Russia at  
OL,6, the British embassy in Berlin was      
OL,7, driven by an intense hatred for his    
OL,8, country, a court has heard.            
OL,10,FBriton David Ballantyne Smith, 58,     
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to eight charges last   
OL,12,Fyear but returned to court for legal   
OL,13,Fargument about his motivation.         
OL,15,FSmith is alleged to have received money
OL,16,Fin exchange for information.           
OL,18,FHe claims he was not paid and was      
OL,19,Fmotivated by an employment grievance   
OL,20,Fwhile suffering mental health issues.  
